{
  "stem": "5516.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They used to go there by 20 years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he used to teach me, you know-- Mhm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--how to do the bar mitzvah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, just in the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have in this time hotels, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh-huh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father invited the, the synagogue's members, you know, who was in, in the synagogue in this Saturday.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He invite in the house, and-- Did you have that-- your bar mitzvah-- in your father's synagogue?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did he have it then?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We was close to all of them, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But one thing is I was close to the youngest one, very close.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, he's now in Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in California.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Israel.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We was-- before the war, we didn't have too much trouble between the Jews and non-Jews because the president [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] of Lithuania was very good to Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was elected president, but it's not like in United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The mayors of the cities used to elect him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, but the only thing, when they established Lithuania in 1918 after the First World War, the United Nation declared all the countries was occupied by Russian, they used to be released-- that they released Lithuania, too.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they made a, a government there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this president was President Antanas Smetona.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was there for six months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after six months, somebody took over the government, like now in South America, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He took over the government.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was, like, a little bit communism, you know, like a socialist, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He took it over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He took it over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he didn't do nothing to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He released him, just took away the job from him when they took him out.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
